        "\n",
        "\n",
        "# What This First Submission Should Demonstrate\n",
        "\n",
        "By the end of Milestone 1, your team should show:\n",
        "\n",
        "- Clear domain scoping\n",
        "- Understanding of SEC structural segmentation\n",
